    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Passenger Terminal Complex\nALLENTOWN-BETHLEHEM-EASTON AIRPORT,\nLehigh Valley, Pa.\nLocated within a few minutes from the three\ncities, it is owned and operated by the Lehigh-\nNorthampton Airport Authority and sponsored by\nthe Counties of Lehigh and Northampton. Started\nin 1929, it is one of the older airports in the east.\n3,5\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nKARDMASTER BROCHURES® Allentown, Pa.\nPost Card\n015.166.2033"
    ],
